Item description without its partner:

Wondrous item, uncommon (requires attunement)

Counts as a Silvered Longsword +1
    Versatile
    1d8 (1d10) Slashing damage

This item was forged as a symbol of a dwarven and elven alliance. 

Item description with its partner

Wondrous item, uncommon

Counts as a Silvered Longsword +1
    Versatile
    1d8 (1d10) Slashing damage

This item was forged as a symbol of a dwarven and elven alliance. When the weilder is within 30 feet of the Axe of Elfsong they gain the following benefits:

Your Constitution score increases by 2, to a maximum of 20
You have advantage on saving throws against poison and you have resistance against poison damage
You have darkvision out to a range of 60 feet
You can speak, read, and write Dwarvish